    <div class="note"><strong>A service, not a subscription.</strong> We don't sell seats. We look at how your office works, build software that fits it, and put it in place with you — drawing on how peer institutions handle the same work. A fixed-scope, one-time engagement with a clear timeline — not an open-ended budget — and you own the result.</div>

